headline: ROLLINS, INC. SCHEDULES DATE FOR RELEASE OF FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL YEAR 2025 FINANCIAL RESULTS
summary: Rollins, Inc. (NYSE:ROL) ("Rollins" or the "Company"), a premier global consumer and commercial services company, today announced that it will release its fourth quarter and full year results for the period ended December 31, 2025, after the market closes on Wednesday, February 11, 2026. In conjunction with its release, the Company will host a conference call to review the Company's financial and operating results before the market opens on Thursday, February 12, 2026, at 8:30 a.m. Eastern Time.
